[h3 id=StageByStageComments 
	" Stage by stage comments
	$LF
]h3
[h4 id=CityAndConstructionSite 
	" City and Construction Site
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"There's one energy capsule hidden in a sewer and other in the roof of a house,
	$LF
	"in terms of "collecting", the roof one is faster but the time saved by running
	$LF
	"compensates the time spent to collect the one in the sewer.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=TyrannusLabyrinth 
	" Tyrannus' Labyrinth
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"The first time I used the Stop 'n' Go glitch to delay some enemies,
	$LF
	"but sometimes it's faster to take damage.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=LeaderSFortress 
	" Leader's Fortress
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"This is the only level that is possible to pass through walls,
	$LF
	"(not all of them though) and it was used twice to save time.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=LeaderSInterior 
	" Leader's Interior
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"Oh man, this level is a pain! There's too much platforms here and
	$LF
	"Hulk's jump animation is slow so, I try to avoid it at all costs,
	$LF
	"I even take damage to make him land sooner, but well...
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=FinalConfrontation 
	" Final Confrontation
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"This level is frenetic! Hulk even become invincible to keep the pace,
	$LF
	"but that's not excuse to take damage all the time if you ask me.
	$LF
]div
[h3 id=Bosses 
	" Bosses
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"Except for the Leader, all bosses have the same strategy, run towards them then hit them with Hulk's head.
	$LF
]div
[h3 id=TricksAndGlitches 
	" Tricks and Glitches
	$LF
]h3
[h4 id=StopNGoGlitch 
	" Stop 'n' Go glitch
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"Hulk must run for one frame then stop for one frame,
	$LF
	"this glitch delays some events in the game.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=PassThroughWalls 
	" Pass Through Walls
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"Hulk must grab an enemy that is really close to a wall.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=Invincibility 
	" Invincibility
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"Hulk must die and take damage afterwards, or suicide
	$LF
	"before the next level and then take damage.(X+Y+Start)
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=ElevatorGlitch 
	" Elevator glitch
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"If the elevator is going up, jump for one frame,
	$LF
	"Hulk falls through the elevator floor.(not used)
	$LF
]div
